== 制作 ==
第一集，也就是试播集是由David S. Goyer（另外他也导演了本集）和Brannon Braga所撰写的。剧本由[[罗伯特·J·索耶|罗伯特·J·索耶]]同名小说改编，Goyer和Braga作为[[执行制片人|执行制片人]]，另外还有Jessica Boesiczky Goyer, Vince Gerardis以及Ralph Vicinanza.<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/tvnews.php?id=49023| title=Flash Forward New Companion for Lost| publisher=www.comingsoon.net| accessdate=2008-08-09| archive-date=2014-08-09| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140809101443/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/tvnews.php?id=49023| dead-url=no}}</ref> 

''未来闪影''原本计划在[[HBO|HBO]]播出，但后来它认为广播网络会更适合这部电视剧，因此卖掉了播出权。2009年5月[[美国广播公司|ABC]]安排了试映之后预定了十三集。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3i4b5caa365ad73b3a562218379433fee4 |title=The Hollywood Reporter |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2009-05-08 |accessdate=2009-09-25 |archive-date=2009-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090514024120/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3i4b5caa365ad73b3a562218379433fee4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2009年10月12日，[[美国广播公司|ABC]]将第一季的集数增加到22集。当日晚些时候又宣布会追加三集的订阅，增加到25集，继而又调整到了24集，而实际播出仍然是22集。<ref name="24 episodes">{{cite web |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news.aspx?id=8416 |title=ABC Confirms Episode Orders |publisher=The Futon Critic |date=2009-12-08 |accessdate=2009-12-04 |archive-date=2020-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609081053/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news.aspx?id=8416 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118009832.html?categoryId=14&cs=1 |title=ABC picks up more 'FlashForward' |publisher=''[[綜藝|綜藝]]'' |first=Stuart |last=Levine |date=2009-10-12 |accessdate=2009-10-14 |archive-date=2010-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100325130722/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118009832.html?categoryid=14&cs=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ausiellofiles.ew.com/2009/10/12/this-just-in-flash-forward-gets-full-season/ |title=This just in: 'FlashForward' gets full season |publisher=''[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]'' |author=[[Michael_Ausiello|Michael Ausiello]] |work=The Ausiello Files |date=2009-10-12 |accessdate=2009-10-12 |archive-date=2009-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091016043717/http://ausiellofiles.ew.com/2009/10/12/this-just-in-flash-forward-gets-full-season/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/10/12/abc-orders-full-season-of-flashforward/ |title=ABC Orders Full Season of 'FlashForward' |publisher=''[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]'' |work=ArtsBeat: The Culture at Large |last=Itzkoff |first=Dave |date=2009-10-12 |accessdate=2009-10-12 |archive-date=2015-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610232614/http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/10/12/abc-orders-full-season-of-flashforward/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

