传言称[[Starz|Starz]]电视台会考虑购买未来闪影的版权并有可能更新第二季。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tvsquad.com/2010/07/23/is-flashforward-heading-to-starz/ |title=Is 'FlashForward' Heading to Starz? |work=TV Squad |date=2010-07-23 |accessdate=2010-09-06 |archive-date=2010-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100907015409/http://www.tvsquad.com/2010/07/23/is-flashforward-heading-to-starz |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://scifimafia.com/2010/07/flashforward-might-be-saved-by-starz/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-09-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100807001720/http://scifimafia.com/2010/07/flashforward-might-be-saved-by-starz/ |archivedate=2010-08-07 }}</ref>

