=== 收视率 ===
尽管未来闪影的第一集在美国取得了收视人数1247万的好成绩，第一季结束时的收视率仍然迅速降到了三分之一的水平。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/03/28/flashforwards-ratings-blame-the-show-not-the-scheduling/46408 |title=Updated: "FlashForward's"; Ratings: Blame the Show, Not the Scheduling |last1=Seidman |first1=Robert |date=March 28, 2010 |work=tvbythenumbers.com |publisher=TVbytheNumbers |accessdate=June 5, 2010 |archive-date=2010-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100401062529/http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/03/28/flashforwards-ratings-blame-the-show-not-the-scheduling/46408 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 未来闪影在美国的播放时间由于太晚而受到一些人的诟病。但在其他国家，例如英国，即便是黄金时间播放，收视率仍然大大下降。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s56/flashforward/news/a210358/flashforward-makes-poor-uk-return.html|title=FlashForward makes poor ratings return|date=March 24, 2010|work=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|accessdate=May 5, 2010|archive-date=2010-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100506002159/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s56/flashforward/news/a210358/flashforward-makes-poor-uk-return.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

